                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H3" class="mt-6">PaginationList and PaginationItem</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    <code class="font-semibold">PaginationList</code> and <code class="font-semibold">PaginationItem</code> are structural wrappers. They primarily accept
                    <code class="font-semibold">ChildContent</code> and pass through additional HTML attributes.
                </RzParagraph>

                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H3" class="mt-6">PaginationLink</RzHeading>
