                                <td class="px-4 py-4"><code class="font-mono font-medium text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400">ChildContent</code></td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400"><code>RenderFragment?</code> – Visible content of the link, typically a page number.</td>
